                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/16673.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Agent <persName type="from">Carothers</persName> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Douglas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-11-02T18:00:00-07:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 2, 1915—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Villa has moved up more artillery. Desultory firing has already commenced.
                    General Funston held short conference with Villa this morning.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Carothers.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
